=Episode 24=

00:00:57.373 --> 00:00:59.852
Grand Frontier General He Chen,

00:01:00.133 --> 00:01:02.652
presents birthday tributes
and requesting audience.

00:01:09.452 --> 00:01:11.732
Greetings, Your Majesty.

00:01:12.292 --> 00:01:15.893
Long live Your Majesty.

00:01:21.773 --> 00:01:23.310
I have long dwelled on the battlefield,

00:01:23.693 --> 00:01:25.533
armor has never left my body.

00:01:25.690 --> 00:01:27.133
It is truly inconvenient to kneel.

00:01:27.732 --> 00:01:30.613
I beg Your Majesty to forgive
my breach of etiquette.

00:01:31.292 --> 00:01:33.133
General, you are a pillar of Great Liang.

00:01:33.812 --> 00:01:36.092
Such empty formalities need not matter.

00:01:36.350 --> 00:01:38.092
Thank you
for Your Majesty's understanding.

00:01:39.493 --> 00:01:42.133
I heard Your Majesty's birthday
is approaching,

00:01:42.413 --> 00:01:44.613
thus I have specially brought
a generous gift.

00:01:45.012 --> 00:01:45.493
Come.

00:01:50.372 --> 00:01:51.812
This item is called Dongzhu pearl.

00:02:03.932 --> 00:02:04.572
He Chen.

00:02:05.053 --> 00:02:06.773
What do you mean by this?

00:02:08.493 --> 00:02:10.613
I dare to speak a word of offense.

00:02:11.270 --> 00:02:14.092
Has Your Majesty not been investigating
the Shen family's Dongzhu pearl?

00:02:14.692 --> 00:02:16.092
I have brought it to you.

00:02:18.212 --> 00:02:19.053
In this world,

00:02:20.293 --> 00:02:22.812
there is no such thing as Dongzhu pearl.

00:02:23.812 --> 00:02:24.692
I say

00:02:25.333 --> 00:02:26.453
this is Dongzhu pearl.

00:02:26.812 --> 00:02:28.132
Then this is Dongzhu pearl.

00:02:36.692 --> 00:02:37.613
Thank you

00:02:39.092 --> 00:02:40.493
for finding this pearl for me.

00:02:41.013 --> 00:02:42.932
This is my duty.

00:02:45.812 --> 00:02:47.013
Recently I heard

00:02:48.013 --> 00:02:51.453
Your Majesty is troubled
by Qin Moxiu killing Zhu Lv

00:02:51.573 --> 00:02:52.573
and worries endlessly.

00:02:53.450 --> 00:02:55.252
I am willing
to share Your Majesty's burden

00:02:55.692 --> 00:02:57.412
and personally interrogate
this criminal.

00:03:01.212 --> 00:03:02.987
(Imperial Garden, Jingxin Pavilion)

00:03:11.773 --> 00:03:13.412
These two were once under your command.

00:03:13.972 --> 00:03:16.773
Now they serve under General Li Wei.

00:03:17.173 --> 00:03:19.293
My Lord, pray do not mind.

00:03:22.293 --> 00:03:23.092
How would I dare?

00:03:34.493 --> 00:03:35.212
Please.

00:03:46.853 --> 00:03:48.453
My Lord is so sharp,

00:03:48.932 --> 00:03:52.132
truly quite reminiscent of General Qin.

00:03:52.173 --> 00:03:54.652
You dog of a traitor aren't worthy
to mention my father's name.

00:03:55.092 --> 00:03:56.013
If not for you

00:03:56.013 --> 00:03:57.333
using a non-existent Dongzhu pearl

00:03:57.333 --> 00:03:58.710
to frame the Qin and Shen families,

00:04:00.053 --> 00:04:01.532
how would you have today's power?

00:04:02.773 --> 00:04:04.692
My Lord, this world

00:04:07.013 --> 00:04:09.132
is written by the victors.

00:04:10.252 --> 00:04:11.773
If I say Dongzhu pearl can fund armies,

00:04:11.773 --> 00:04:12.532
then it can.

00:04:13.412 --> 00:04:15.212
If I say the Fengling Army
is a demon army,

00:04:15.853 --> 00:04:16.932
then they are.

00:04:17.452 --> 00:04:20.892
I know how to read the tides
of the time.

00:04:23.210 --> 00:04:24.828
Using Lady's Pavilion
to collect wealth,

00:04:24.852 --> 00:04:26.490
and the Mid-Month
Banquet to gather factions.

00:04:26.533 --> 00:04:28.973
I've never seen anyone
describe such filthy deeds

00:04:29.533 --> 00:04:31.533
so righteously.

00:04:40.053 --> 00:04:41.853
Before your father died,

00:04:42.173 --> 00:04:44.252
he was just as naive as you.

00:04:45.372 --> 00:04:46.372
What I am gaining

00:04:47.372 --> 00:04:50.053
is a country already within my grasp.

00:04:50.853 --> 00:04:54.093
You thought you killed Zhu Lv
to uphold justice,

00:04:54.293 --> 00:04:57.413
but you merely removed a threat for me.

00:04:58.692 --> 00:05:00.853
My men are already
in the Imperial Study.

00:05:01.533 --> 00:05:03.012
Once midnight passes,

00:05:03.493 --> 00:05:06.812
you will die by my blade

00:05:06.973 --> 00:05:08.973
accused of poisoning the Emperor.

00:05:14.692 --> 00:05:15.692
Who allowed you in?

00:05:17.493 --> 00:05:19.053
Greetings, Your Majesty.

00:05:19.413 --> 00:05:21.012
By order of the Grand Frontier General,

00:05:21.020 --> 00:05:22.760
I present birthday wine
from the Western Regions

00:05:22.772 --> 00:05:25.132
to congratulate Your Majesty
on eternal longevity.

00:05:26.692 --> 00:05:28.132
Convey my thanks to the general.

00:05:29.173 --> 00:05:29.733
Set it there.

00:05:30.213 --> 00:05:32.132
This wine is a fifty-year vintage.

00:05:32.613 --> 00:05:34.053
The general instructed me

00:05:34.332 --> 00:05:36.452
that Your Majesty must finish it.

00:05:38.372 --> 00:05:38.973
Your Majesty.

00:05:39.533 --> 00:05:40.213
Please drink.

00:05:40.310 --> 00:05:41.053
What are you doing?

00:05:41.100 --> 00:05:41.880
What are you doing?

00:05:42.653 --> 00:05:43.053
Guards!

00:05:44.093 --> 00:05:44.853
He Chen.

00:05:45.533 --> 00:05:47.853
Do you really think Heaven will tolerate

00:05:47.932 --> 00:05:49.533
a traitor as faithless as you?

00:05:50.053 --> 00:05:51.973
Did you truly think I didn't know

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:53.772
that this is a play you
and the young Emperor

00:05:53.932 --> 00:05:55.613
put on together?

00:05:56.012 --> 00:05:57.093
To lure me into the capital,

00:05:57.572 --> 00:06:00.493
then send the White Tiger Guard
and the Black Armor Army

00:06:00.653 --> 00:06:01.533
to surround me.

00:06:02.173 --> 00:06:03.230
I have already sent troops

00:06:03.613 --> 00:06:05.613
to block their path into the capital.

00:06:06.053 --> 00:06:07.692
Tonight, all of you will die.

00:06:10.213 --> 00:06:11.252
But it seems

00:06:12.132 --> 00:06:13.252
you overlooked one army.

00:06:14.892 --> 00:06:18.413
An army you personally destroyed.

00:06:18.572 --> 00:06:19.132
Let go!

00:06:20.252 --> 00:06:20.892
Your Majesty.

00:06:21.932 --> 00:06:22.932
Please drink now.

00:06:29.572 --> 00:06:30.093
Your Majesty.

00:06:46.053 --> 00:06:47.132
State Preceptor He.

00:06:48.270 --> 00:06:49.293
Under my father's command,

00:06:49.310 --> 00:06:51.670
there was Fengling Army
with glorious battle achievements.

00:06:52.132 --> 00:06:54.053
You guarded against
every registered army,

00:06:54.812 --> 00:06:56.012
yet you forgot

00:06:56.413 --> 00:06:59.053
the Fengling Army
that you personally destroyed.

00:06:59.132 --> 00:07:00.173
General.

00:07:00.190 --> 00:07:01.290
The assassination attempt
has been exposed!

00:07:01.300 --> 00:07:02.360
Someone is bringing troops over!

00:07:02.372 --> 00:07:03.173
Impossible.

00:07:03.572 --> 00:07:05.173
I've been shrewd all my life,

00:07:05.653 --> 00:07:08.932
never thought I would overlook
this group of rascals.

00:07:09.493 --> 00:07:12.572
I should have slaughtered
them all long ago.

00:07:56.932 --> 00:07:57.932
My Lord, don't kill me!

00:07:58.000 --> 00:07:59.990
Listen to me first.
Kill me afterward if you must.

00:08:00.252 --> 00:08:01.332
You have already inherited

00:08:01.350 --> 00:08:03.290
the title of Marquis Wu'an
from the old general.

00:08:03.452 --> 00:08:04.493
If you kill me now,

00:08:04.710 --> 00:08:06.413
you'll only get a bit more reward
at most.

00:08:06.653 --> 00:08:08.012
It may even cause that Emperor

00:08:08.020 --> 00:08:10.150
to suspect that your merits
overshadow his authority.

00:08:12.772 --> 00:08:13.613
Go on.

00:08:15.173 --> 00:08:16.450
Why don't you and I join forces

00:08:16.653 --> 00:08:17.892
and kill the Emperor together?

00:08:18.293 --> 00:08:19.413
We can share the world!

00:08:19.452 --> 00:08:19.932
No.

00:08:20.653 --> 00:08:23.452
I am willing to support you
as the new Emperor.

00:08:24.132 --> 00:08:26.132
I will guard the border
for the new sovereign

00:08:26.190 --> 00:08:27.990
and protect the nation forever.
How about that?

00:08:43.532 --> 00:08:44.012
You...

00:08:44.213 --> 00:08:44.813
My Lord.

00:08:45.093 --> 00:08:45.892
You must believe me.

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:47.820
I will definitely help you
ascend the throne.

00:08:47.853 --> 00:08:49.333
Wealth, power, and honor,

00:08:49.652 --> 00:08:50.973
I can get them all for you!

00:08:51.252 --> 00:08:52.790
Then you will be worth more than gold.

00:08:52.813 --> 00:08:54.132
The whole world will be yours.

00:08:54.170 --> 00:08:55.453
Anything you want, you will have!

00:08:55.813 --> 00:08:56.412
Don't kill me!

00:08:56.652 --> 00:08:57.132
Don't!

00:09:00.892 --> 00:09:03.252
You paved your path to power
with the blood of women,

00:09:04.132 --> 00:09:05.532
treating human lives like weeds.

00:09:06.532 --> 00:09:08.733
Today, I will use your blood

00:09:09.252 --> 00:09:10.613
to cleanse this filthy world.

00:09:36.372 --> 00:09:37.213
Half an inch further,

00:09:37.310 --> 00:09:38.613
and you would've lost your life.

00:09:39.652 --> 00:09:41.012
You know I can protect myself.

00:09:42.210 --> 00:09:43.613
You shouldn't have been so reckless.

00:09:45.733 --> 00:09:46.252
It's fine.

00:09:47.532 --> 00:09:48.613
Just a minor wound.

00:09:49.213 --> 00:09:50.450
A few days of rest will heal it.

00:10:32.132 --> 00:10:32.933
It's been ten years.

00:10:34.933 --> 00:10:36.693
Every day and night in these ten years,

00:10:40.500 --> 00:10:42.690
I have lived in the torment
of my father's blood feud.

00:10:49.733 --> 00:10:50.813
Until I met you.

00:10:53.172 --> 00:10:53.813
Thank you.

00:11:00.693 --> 00:11:03.252
For being willing to walk
with me on the edge of danger.

00:11:08.012 --> 00:11:10.292
Now that my long-held wish is fulfilled.

00:11:11.733 --> 00:11:12.333
From now on,

00:11:15.190 --> 00:11:16.573
will you continue to walk with me?

00:12:04.973 --> 00:12:05.625
(A Household of Chastity)
The Case of

00:12:05.649 --> 00:12:06.292
(A Household of Chastity)
the Liu Clan's Martyr Heroines

00:12:07.213 --> 00:12:08.813
is truly a sin of mine.

00:12:10.493 --> 00:12:12.292
Today I restore Shen Wanqing's status,

00:12:12.973 --> 00:12:15.333
and order the Three Judicial Offices
to retry the case.

00:12:16.372 --> 00:12:19.252
The truth shall be sent
to all county yamen

00:12:19.252 --> 00:12:19.973
(A Household of Chastity)

00:12:19.973 --> 00:12:21.333
to warn the world.

00:12:29.490 --> 00:12:32.270
I heard His Majesty just granted you
the title of Duke of the Nation.

00:12:32.493 --> 00:12:34.390
Are you truly willing to give up
such prospects

00:12:34.973 --> 00:12:36.172
to enjoy the world with me?

00:12:37.790 --> 00:12:39.573
What are those empty honors
compared to you?

00:13:21.250 --> 00:13:24.987
(The End)